>)、玉山金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2884:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2884\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2884-TW</a>)、大聯大 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3702:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3702\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3702-TW</a>)、遠傳 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4904:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4904\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4904-TW</a>)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>3. 投信當日 (19) 賣超的股票<br/>華新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>)、國巨 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2327:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2327\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2327-TW</a>)、大聯大 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3702:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3702\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3702-TW</a>)、南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)、台泥 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1101:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1101\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1101-TW</a>)<br/> </p></section></main>",
